Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN UPDATE Bills SET InterestAmount = CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(DAY, DueDate, GETDATE()) > 0 THEN (TotalPayable * (SELECT TOP 1 Rate FROM InterestRates WHERE DaysOverdue <= DATEDIFF(DAY, DueDate, GETDATE()) ORDER BY DaysOverdue DESC) / 100) ELSE 0 END, TotalWithInterest = TotalPayable + ISNULL(InterestAmount, 0) WHERE PaymentStatus = 'Pending' AND DATEDIFF(DAY, DueDate, GETDATE()) > 0; END;
